Usage: displayBufTree [-help] -net <net name> [-outfile <file name>]

-help                    # Prints out the command usage
-net <net name>          # Specifies the name of the net for which you want to
                         # display the buffer tree (string, required)
-outfile <file name>     # Specifies the text file in which output would be
                         # generated (string, optional)